d":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泛民支持者全部唔出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見有d泛民fans都開始理解到民主黨既本質<br />\n呢個係一個十分好既現象</blockquote><br />\n舊有既共同體已經喪失識別敵人同自我修服既能力<br />\n核心層不再具有自知之明既能力<br />\n即將面臨土崩瓦解既命運<br />\n<br />\n餘下既人若仍猶豫不決, 仍未肯自我進化成斷腸草<br />\n一律變成絕情花既食糧</blockquote><br />\n愈早做選擇，代價愈低<br />\n愈遲做選擇，代價愈高<br />\n千古不變既定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8972b78c28f8dc8bc95b80613beccc1bcb1ea410","tid":324291,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5579002cff73cac598eab40654cbfe556a98a251","tid":324291,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:36:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b6fce63390d994c3c01c61618c0e89c10081f495","tid":324291,"uid":96964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"有新泛民本土派被人DQ 民主黨公民黨不知幾開心 又多幾個議席<br />\n<br />\n你當佢地係建制派就得"},{"pid":"4428798920b7231559a4f672a0f24fa94176dd61","tid":324291,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfc5caf55527356cb6e1a1069a8c1c96c8349e8","tid":324291,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有新泛民本土派被人DQ 民主黨公民黨不知幾開心 又多幾個議席<br />\n<br />\n你當佢地係建制派就得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0dedd75b8aa08efa7931b1faa214661c9fe917","tid":324291,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"其實